# {{ .ProjectName }} — Memory Index

> The durable, version-controlled memory graph for this repo. Notes are small,
> linkable markdown files under `Memory/decisions/` and `Memory/notes/`. Unlike
> the agent's session working memory, this graph is a permanent record meant to
> be read back — and aggregated by downstream tooling — long after the work ships.

Each note follows the project note schema: see
[Playbook/Standards/NoteStandards.md](Playbook/Standards/NoteStandards.md) for the
frozen frontmatter and body format (`schema_version`, `permalink`, `scope`,
Observations / Relations).

